{{Infobox dungeon |name = Digletts Cave |image = [[File:Digletts Cave.png|thumb]] |caption = An overhead map of Digletts Cave. |tokens = 95 |location = North of Viridian Forest, on Route 2. }} '''Digletts Cave''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kanto]]. It has 25 tiles arranged in a 5x5 square, including 5 chest tiles, 13 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 1,208 HP.
